1034
00:38:39.124 --> 00:38:43.827
♪ Oh-oh-oh. oh-oh-oh. ohhhhhhhhh ♪

1035
00:38:43.829 --> 00:38:45.328
Hey.

1036
00:38:45.330 --> 00:38:46.729
Hey.

1037
00:38:46.731 --> 00:38:48.131
♪ Oh-oh-oh. oh-oh-oh ♪

1038
00:38:48.133 --> 00:38:49.399
I screwed up.

1039
00:38:49.401 --> 00:38:50.934
♪ Ohhhhhhhhh ♪

1040
00:38:50.936 --> 00:38:53.002
Yeah. You did.

1041
00:38:53.004 --> 00:38:57.740
♪ How many times can
you fall on your knees ♪

1042
00:38:57.742 --> 00:38:59.043
Come in.

1043
00:39:00.679 --> 00:39:03.680
