1047
00:39:10.989 --> 00:39:13.323
You're one of the toughest
women I've ever met.

1048
00:39:13.325 --> 00:39:15.425
The last thing you need is a protector.

1049
00:39:15.427 --> 00:39:18.695
and I didn't mean to imply that you did.

1050
00:39:18.697 --> 00:39:20.431
♪ ... I've never seen ♪

1051
00:39:20.433 --> 00:39:21.455
I'm sorry.

1052
00:39:21.457 --> 00:39:23.176
