1053
00:39:23.178 --> 00:39:24.200
Thanks.

1054
00:39:24.202 --> 00:39:25.935
♪ I believe. I believe... ♪

1055
00:39:25.937 --> 00:39:27.370
I accept your apology.

1056
00:39:27.372 --> 00:39:29.172
♪ ... soon ♪

1057
00:39:29.174 --> 00:39:30.306
Really?

1058
00:39:30.308 --> 00:39:31.875
♪ I believe. I believe. I believe ♪

1059
00:39:31.877 --> 00:39:33.309
Yes.

1060
00:39:33.311 --> 00:39:34.777
Yes.

1061
00:39:34.779 --> 00:39:36.179
♪ I'll get there soon ♪

1062
00:39:36.181 --> 00:39:39.149
♪♪

1063
00:39:39.151 --> 00:39:41.317
You gotta get out of here.

1064
00:39:41.319 --> 00:39:44.020
♪ I've been trying ♪

1065
00:39:44.022 --> 00:39:46.022
Alright.

1066
00:39:46.024 --> 00:39:47.457
Whatever you say. boss.

1067
00:39:47.459 --> 00:39:49.893
[BOTH CHUCKLE]

1068
00:39:49.895 --> 00:39:51.327
Will I see you tomorrow?

1069
00:39:51.329 --> 00:39:52.896
Yeah. Yeah.

1070
00:39:52.898 --> 00:39:53.997
Cool.

1071
00:39:53.999 --> 00:39:55.999
♪♪

1072
00:39:56.001 --> 00:39:58.735
♪ And everything ♪

1073
00:39:58.737 --> 00:40:03.306
♪ That ever slipped right by me ♪

1074
00:40:03.308 --> 00:40:06.042
♪ Was it ever really meant to be ♪

1075
00:40:06.044 --> 00:40:10.914
♪ Or was it just bad timing? ♪

1076
00:40:10.916 --> 00:40:18.221
♪ I believe. I believe.
I believe I'll get there soon ♪

1077
00:40:18.223 --> 00:40:25.328
♪ I believe. I believe.
I believe I'll get there soon ♪

1078
00:40:25.330 --> 00:40:26.429
♪ I can see... ♪

1079
00:40:26.431 --> 00:40:27.630
