1100
00:41:06.953 --> 00:41:09.906
because Serj is gonna
walk for Chris's murder.

1101
00:41:09.908 --> 00:41:16.380
♪ I believe. I believe.
I believe I'll get there soon ♪

1102
00:41:17.960 --> 00:41:19.315
