1106
00:41:24.889 --> 00:41:27.541
<i>Name names. okay? Just testify.</i>

1107
00:41:27.543 --> 00:41:28.632
<i>- Armstrong.
- No!</i>

1108
00:41:28.634 --> 00:41:30.267
- [<i>GUNSHOTS</i>]
- [KEYBOARD CLACKS]

1109
00:41:31.129 --> 00:41:32.895
<i>- Armstrong.
- [KEYBOARD CLACKS]</i>

1110
00:41:32.897 --> 00:41:35.398
She said his name before she saw him.

1111
00:41:35.400 --> 00:41:39.400
♪♪

1112
00:41:43.441 --> 00:41:47.441
♪♪

1113
00:41:51.107 --> 00:41:52.796
